Package: moneca
Title: Mobility Network Clustering Analysis with Auto-Tuning
Description: moneca creates a weighted network from a mobility table and uses cliques (or similar) to create discrete and nested clusters. Features comprehensive auto-tuning capabilities for parameter optimization including stability-based, quality-based, performance-balanced, Pareto multi-objective, and cross-validation methods. This is a maintained fork of the original MONECA package with modernized visualizations, comprehensive testing, enhanced documentation, and advanced optimization features.
URL: https://github.com/gmontaletti/moneca
Version: 0.8.1
Maintainer: Giampaolo Montaletti <giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com>
